Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural Hot Spring \N Beauty Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please meet up with us in front of \Nthe bathhouse at twelve o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't have minded camping out, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you'd have money \Nif you could get to an ATM?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that I'd bought the latest carton.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a festival going on nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... wanna go to the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in good spirits, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublime Bath 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublime Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...?\NSublime Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublime Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Trickstar\NEncounter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The recording from when you went to \Nthe Ezo Fair was magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother... do you not... hate him? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother... do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother... do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother... do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother... do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! You can stop!\NYour big brother... do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your big brother... do you not... hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, expanding on the topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm keeping you close at hand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is so that I can decide \Nhow you will be dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying to hide the truth your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I deem it necessary, I could even create \Nan opportunity to reintroduce you as her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't do anything uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...are we taking a detour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I heard the hotel we're staying at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is really close and on a straight road \Nfrom the shrine we just paid a visit to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but this car has made several turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That, and because you're a magician, Danji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know what \NI'm thinking right now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring to go straight home after work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat something sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing anything uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I am Danji Momoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As Danji Momoyama, \NI want things to go well with Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll decide when it's necessary to act on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how they were sold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The guarana soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I searched around, \Nbut I couldn't find it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural Hot Spring \N Beauty Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But to make up for that, I found a yummy \Nlimited parfait they sell here in Mino.\NNatural Hot Spring \N Beauty Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I love parfaits!\NNatural Hot Spring \N Beauty Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't use the baths, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just go in to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublime Bath 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they must be good people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And, uh... who is this young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... she's my employer... so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And wait, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you kinda dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... stuff kinda happened, \Nand now we're penniless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even afford a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji, let's pay for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After your bath, let's eat parfaits together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji seems in good spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems rough for Miss Minae, \Nthough, not being able to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd your good spirits go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I am in good spirits! \NI'm getting the bath I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...I feel like I've seen her somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excited about the parfait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently recruiting friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's be friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even treating us to parfaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been called that in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man, you really saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even covering our travel expenses... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can get back to Kaga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're not going back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? On that note, \Nwhy did you guys come out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're headed for the headquarters of Daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On our way here, we've been \Ncrushing Daybreak's team hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the other teams are cooperating \Nwith us, in order to stop Daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Drumroll, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's Mino's specialty, \NMoo-Moo Hida Dairy Parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me \Nwhat was going on with Blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'd better make absolutely sure \Nthat they don't find out they're mutual enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you both play Vanguard, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on a team or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Kaga's own--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... a lovely garden over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathing in the morning is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford anything here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hear festival sounds again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Some sort of explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fireworks, right? \NThere's a festival in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. The one on the poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Festivals sound like a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you never been to one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'd like to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they can be dangerous, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not dangerous at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As thanks for getting to use the bath... \Nthough I don't think it can match that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better ask Haruka if it's okay to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like the den mother for my team!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Minae, you're also on a... team...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone else hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, but maybe \NI'll check out ahead of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What lovely weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just try out the stone sauna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I play Vanguard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both impressive, \Npacking away a second parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You two... really seem similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They make a cute pair, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you've got some on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, something else! \NLet's talk about something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... ask me a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Miss Minae, if you're also on a team--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why do you both keep \Nbreaking off in the middle of sentences?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,SHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll ask you a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Which team do you belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's been with you, Danji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep derailing the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both members of Blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Blackout full of bad people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I sure can't wait for the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackout is a bad team that keeps \Ninterfering with Daybreak's activities!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, hasn't Daybreak been \Nburning a bunch of teams' banners?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because those banners belonged to bad teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, because Blackout instigated them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the bad teams are all trying \Nto get in Daybreak's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackout is the boss of the bad teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"The boss"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone's the boss of bad teams, it's Daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the festival! The fireworks are amazing!\NIf anyone's the boss of bad teams, it's Daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Daybreak is working towards an environment \Nwhere everybody can fight equally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, these flutes! Such sweet flute sounds!\NDaybreak is working towards an environment \Nwhere everybody can fight equally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, there's a boom! Fireworks!\NWhat's bad about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The shrine's booming, too!\NYou're mistaken about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am not mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, and take a look at--\NNo, I am not mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what Blackout does at times like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll settle this with a Cardfight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is here okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be assisting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fight the way you usually do, Yu-yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All set up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Rino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He discards Cho Kuu Sha \Nfrom his hand, and rides Rino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rino? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Namorkahr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With its skill, I add Swayanbuh \Nfrom my deck to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how... \NYou identify them with stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My Vanguard attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage check... Arcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, you memorize all the cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Reiyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,With Rino's skill, I call Trickstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Back left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Minae...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...did you used to have Trickstar in your--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was noth--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I did used to have Trickstar in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally hilarious, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a stratagem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An attempt to bewilder me with laughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to act nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Danji's friends, \Nso they couldn't be bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, sorry? Maybe you \Nshould look for a different team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask? I'm just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,OverDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when people are in conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it really does work best to resolve it with cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this way, we can become better friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're playing the same game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those stickers? \NAren't they against the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can go to the festival together, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll play there instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally seen... your defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I ride Bavsargra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I place Aadhitya as Right Deity Arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Its skill activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,During this turn, I can Arm an\Nadditional Order card. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Swayanbuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bavsargra's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I retire all my opponent's front row rear-guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it gets an extra critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I call!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bavsargra attacks your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Halibadra attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Halibadra attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona Ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With Nirvana's skill, I call \NTrickstar from the Drop Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,OverDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, another overDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Exspecta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Clinch it this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about the conclusion I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On this turn, not a single one \Nof your attacks will get through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And next turn, \NI'll defeat you with a single attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nirvana attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With Swayanbuh's skill, \NBavsargra gets +10,000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exspecta attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Toresa attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's the reason \NI'm having a Cardfight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I place Prithivih as Right Deity Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mow them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Vairina's alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to have that same deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I switched to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this card before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Trickstar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Trickmoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,DressBoost! +20,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll show you real power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next turn, I'll defeat you with a single attack. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bavsargra attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With Prithivih's skill, it gets +10,000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For 48,000 total!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn them to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... about Yu-yu's deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need to say such things about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just past twelve o'clock already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Game Over, Danji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see our queen is furious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna be one of us, \Nyou really need to do better!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Masanori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let us return to Daybreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...Miss Mirei Minae.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Daybreak...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.65,0:23:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirei... Minae...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hello-break, Daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your leader: Mirei!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.81,0:25:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.52,0:25:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:25:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your leader: Mirei!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.25,0:26:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce \Nmy deck's shadow leader, Trickmoon!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.46,0:26:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Trickmoon can use a skill \Nthat only helps Bavsargra: DressBoost! 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.26,0:26:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When boosted this way, Bavsargra gains \N+10,000 power for each card it has armed!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.31,0:26:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Trickmoon is the partner \Nsupporting me from the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.98,0:26:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You say it's similar to some other card?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.13,0:26:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.89,0:26:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My Trickmoon is much more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.68,0:26:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.49,0:26:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Name\NReminiscence 
